Package db

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Database
    The main class and entry-point for the Database.
    DataFile
    Handles reading and writing of tables to and from files.
    Printer
    Handles printing of information for the user.
    Query
    Handles querying of the database.
    Record
    Holds a single record in the database, aka a row.
    ResultTable
    Presents the results of a database query in table format.
    Schema
    Maintains metadata about the database.
    Table
    Stores a collection of records in the database.
